ygData.messageBody:
Yay I have something to contribute!

I noticed a lot of you are suggesting Collars of Undead Protection and the
like for the neck slot. I have a hardly used enchanter I have been smithing
lately with, and one of the new fine steel plate items is the collar which
is 8 ac...probably the best piece really. Mask is 7 ac but I use the guise
instead.

Costwise it is more expensive. Expect to pay anywhere from 80-150p for the
fine plate, whereas the undead protection is usually closer to 15-30p.


-Izzlari Bustamente
Level 29 and counting
Rathe server

Feeling like a god now that I have figured out how to charm kite
